I need more information to make the API call. Can you provide me with the device type you are using, the air quality app's name, and the time of the day when you want to check the air quality in your living area?

For example: {"deviceType": "tablet", "appName": "Environmental Monitor", "time": "every evening"} 

If you prefer a specific time range, for example every weekend from 6 PM to 8 PM, the format would be: {"deviceType": "speaker", "appName": "Air Quality Monitor", "time": "this weekend from 6 PM to 8 PM"}.
